text: Kankakee County is a county located in the state of Illinois. In the 2020 census, it has a population of 107,502. Its county seat is Kankakee. Kankakee County comprises the Kankakee, IL Metropolitan Statistical Area. ==References== Category:Illinois counties Category:1850s establishments in Illinois Category:1853 establishments in the United States
